Catalano.Imaging.Tools

Class FiltersSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Imaging.Tools.FiltersSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBaseInPlace

    public class FiltersSequence
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBaseInPlace
    Release several filters in the sequence.
    Example: 
      
 FiltersSequence fs = new FiltersSequence();
 fs.add(new Grayscale());
 fs.add(new Blur());
 fs.add(new Threshold(150));
 
 fs.applyInPlace(fastBitmap);
